item.title: Hive – landing page
item.dc:creator: stefan@themeisle.com
item.content:encoded:
hive layout

Easy Business Consulting

Start your next website building project with Analog, a premium layout template for Elementor Page Builder

Learn more

Section Subtitle

Creative problem solving

Analog provides a solid design environment for your content, with a modular layout that takes advantage of the flexible building approach of Elementor page builder.

Re-configurable

Easily re-order, customize and tweak every section you see according to your requirements.

Sharp design

Hive has been designed with the finest pixels in town, delivering a design system that scales.

Efficient

Handcrafted and well-thought out, Hive will power up your building workflow for your projects.

Section Subtitle

Engaging sections

Hive is the perfect context for your content, if you are looking for sharp business aesthetics and consistent design language, ready to be enriched with your content.

skill 74% skill skill

Section Subtitle

Lean Structure

Hive is the perfect context for your content, if you are looking for sharp business aesthetics and consistent design language.

  • Mobile Optimized
  • Easily Customize fonts and colors
  • One price, unlimited uses
  • Sharp, modular , consistent design
Purchase layout

Section Subtitle

Styled Elements

The layout provides styled Elementor widgets (elements) that you can easily edit and re-configure via simple drag and drop gestures.

Growth Hacking

Hive has been designed with the finest pixels in town, delivering a design system that scales.

Sharp design

Hive has been designed with the finest pixels in town, delivering a design system that scales.

Another feature

Hive has been designed with the finest pixels in town, delivering a design system that scales.

Section Subtitle

Science matters

Efficient use of shape dividers result in an engaging section that can be used by practically anything. Enrich by adding a custom background image and see how the shape divider interacts with it.

+ 229 % revenue + 18 % productivity - 45 % abandoned carts

Section Subtitle

A layout that flows

We provide lean advise and consulting for small and medium businesses that take their first online steps. Come join us and see how we can help your business grow.

Medium Button

Section Subtitle

Empowering brands

If you have a number of client logos, the sliding carousel gallery below is a great solution.  Simply replace the image logos with your own and top-up your business credibility and social proof.

Section Subtitle

Get in touch

Facebook Twitter Google-plus

Use the default Map widget and add a similar section where people can find your contact info. For extra bonus, display a contact form by adding a shortcode from any popular contact form plugin.

Contact us

  • 0030 123 4556
  • hive@notanalogwp.com
  • hello_hive

Why us

  • Efficient and fast paced
  • Super logical
  • Flexible pricing options

Section Subtitle

Team members

Mary Finns

Co-Founder- CTO

An awesome, inspirational figure that leads and sets the tone.

Facebook Twitter Dribbble

Jason Spears

Co-Founder- CEO

An awesome, inspirational figure that leads and sets the tone.

Facebook Twitter Dribbble

Beth ribbons

Co-Founder- CFO

An awesome, inspirational figure that leads and sets the tone.

Facebook Twitter Dribbble

Section Subtitle

Employee onboarding

Hive gives you plenty of options to display your content. Combine the layout design with the flexibility of Elementor and tailor the struture down to your needs.

"...An absolutely unique experience. Working with Elementor improved my cognitive functions up to 40%. Great tool!..." Jason Stove CBDO
